    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Error: Site4: Darrowdelf Chamber (not Moria Lake)<br>
<br>
Bid between 3-5, Gandalf&#39;s Pipe and Gandalf will be out reasonable early.<br>
<br>
Sam can get Bill the Pony for twilight denial and There and Back again as well as No stranger will also assist. Gimli will also make the underground sites fantastic for you to move through fast.<br>
<br>
Council Courtyard and Aragorn will supply the twilight removal so playing stuff does not sting so much. <br>
<br>
The rest is pipes and countryside. Use Gandalf to heal burdens, and in turn the Shire Country side will heal your Fellowship. Use The Gaffers pipe to get rid of excess twilight.<br>
<br>
After site 5, kill of Gimli to bring yourself back to 4 companions. Try and kill him off when moving to site 6. <br>
<br>
If done right you should run 1-3, 4-6,7,8,9. only run from 7-9 if you can!!!<br>
<br>
This is sufficient to make your opponent suffer!<br>
<br>
The shadow is simple, get as many cost 1 minions out as possible. This should make The Balrog difficult. You can add a few Fill With Fear&#39;s to help kill archery at site 5 with the Balrog if you like, Pinned down otherwise does a nice job. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
